# Vendored M4 runtime libs are BYTE-EXACT artifacts. Their size + sha256 are pinned in lib-manifest.json
# and checked by the air-gap integrity probe. A line-ending normalization on checkout (autocrlf) would
# inflate the byte count of the TEXT libs (web-llm.js, wllama.mjs) and falsely flag them 'oversize'/corrupt.
# Treat everything here as binary so git never touches the bytes.
* -text
*.js  binary
*.mjs binary
*.json binary
*.wasm binary
*.gz  binary
